  <brief_title>Effects of Blood Letting in Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Blood Letting on Insulin Sensitivity and Blood Pressure in Patients With Metabolic Syndrome: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
